      <title>韩国总统尹永康再次逃避戒严令问询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/south-korea-s-yoon-skips-questioning-again-over-martial-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈再次拒绝接受调查人员有关其戒严令的质询，这位陷入困境的领导人试图在弹劾审判中首先为自己辩护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/south-korea-s-yoon-skips-questioning-again-over-martial-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 03:14:24 GMT</pubDate>
