      <title>厄瓜多尔总统竞选期间力争连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/ecuador-s-president-is-angling-to-stay-in-office-during-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺沃亚 (Daniel Noboa) 希望避免在新年竞选活动之前将权力移交给其疏远的副手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/ecuador-s-president-is-angling-to-stay-in-office-during-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 17:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
